file.name: common.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: '1.0.0'
  title: 'Common Data Types'
  description: 'Common Data Types for Test'

paths: {}
components:
  schemas:

    LocationType:
      type: object
      properties:
        lat:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Lat'
        long:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Long'
      required:
        - lat
        - long

    Lat:
      type: integer
    Long:
      type: integer

    SearchResult:
      type: object
      required:
        - simpleTestResults
      properties:
        resultId:
          type: integer
        simpleTestResults:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string


  responses:
    '404':
      description: Not Found
      type: string
